fi.left2die.io
Class Resources

java.lang.Object
  fi.left2die.io.Resources

public class Resources
extends java.lang.Object

Resource class to storage any image or sound resource used in game. By using this class to storage data it prevents images and sound to be loaded from hard disk multiple times. In different places in source code. To add a new resource use addResource method call: Resource.addResource( "helikopterinlapa", new Image("data/images/lapa.png") ); To get a image resource, it gives you a new instance of image resources object: Resources.getImage( "helikopterinlapa" ):

Author:
TeeMuki
